01Gn 44:23 But you told your servants, 'Unless your youngest brother comes down with you, you will not see my face again.'
01Gn 44:24 When we went back to your servant my father, we told him what my lord had said.
01Gn 44:25 "Then our father said, 'Go back and buy a little more food.'
