01Gn 44:32 Your servant guaranteed the boy's safety to my father. I said, 'If I do not bring him back to you, I will bear the blame before you, my father, all my life!'
01Gn 44:33 "Now then, please let your servant remain here as my lord's slave in place of the boy, and let the boy return with his brothers.
