02Ex 16:25 "Eat it today," Moses said, "because today is a Sabbath to the LORD. You will not find any of it on the ground today.
02Ex 16:26 Six days you are to gather it, but on the seventh day, the Sabbath, there will not be any."
02Ex 16:27 Nevertheless, some of the people went out on the seventh day to gather it, but they found none.
02Ex 16:28 Then the LORD said to Moses, "How long will you refuse to keep my commands and my instructions?
