02Ex 16:34 As the LORD commanded Moses, Aaron put the manna in front of the Testimony, that it might be kept.
02Ex 16:35 The Israelites ate manna forty years, until they came to a land that was settled; they ate manna until they reached the border of Canaan.
02Ex 16:36 (An omer is one tenth of an ephah.)
02Ex 17:1 The whole Israelite community set out from the Desert of Sin, traveling from place to place as the LORD commanded. They camped at Rephidim, but there was no water for the people to drink.
