02Ex 40:16 Moses did everything just as the LORD commanded him.
02Ex 40:17 So the tabernacle was set up on the first day of the first month in the second year.
02Ex 40:18 When Moses set up the tabernacle, he put the bases in place, erected the frames, inserted the crossbars and set up the posts.
02Ex 40:19 Then he spread the tent over the tabernacle and put the covering over the tent, as the LORD commanded him.
02Ex 40:20 He took the Testimony and placed it in the ark, attached the poles to the ark and put the atonement cover over it.
02Ex 40:21 Then he brought the ark into the tabernacle and hung the shielding curtain and shielded the ark of the Testimony, as the LORD commanded him.
02Ex 40:22 Moses placed the table in the Tent of Meeting on the north side of the tabernacle outside the curtain
02Ex 40:23 and set out the bread on it before the LORD, as the LORD commanded him.
